<HEAD>London Stocks Decline in Early Trading</HEAD>
<DATELINE>LONDON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Stock prices slipped in early trading Tuesday but
regained some ground as bargain hunters moved into the market.
   Dealers said prices initially declined on mounting interest rate
fears and concerns over the general health of the British economy.
   However, some market watchers said a handful of institutions
