<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The stock market was mixed in light trading
today after opening on a slightly stronger note.
   The Dow Jones average of 30 industrials was down 1.83 points at
2,300.04 after a half-hour of trading at 10 a.m. EST.
   Advancing issues outpaced decliners by about 6 to 5 on the New
