0.40 at 331.80.
   On Monday the Dow Jones industrial average slipped 2.93 to
2,301.87.
   Advancing issues slightly outnumbered declines on the NYSE, with
716 up, 687 down and 549 unchanged.
   Big Board volume totaled 123.99 million shares, against 156.95
million in the previous session.
